reviewText: Great Item - Love It - Would recommend highly.
This is Not wide screen, formated for old style tv view, cut out good parts and distorted others, good movie though
Good movies. Definitely worth the price. If you love any of these movies, then worth buying this multi-pack. Can't go wrong with this purchase.

Disc #1, Side A -- Bull Durham: Widescreen
Disc #1, Side B -- Bull Durham: Full Screen

Disc #2 -- Dances With Wolves: Full Screen

Disc #3, Side A -- No Way Out: Widescreen
Disc #3, Side B -- No Way Out: Full Screen

Well for anyone who doesn't know the description of what are all the movies for the triple feature, you can look at the larger picture and it shows the names of the movies. The movies are Bull Durham, Dances with Wolves and No Way Out.

This is a great deal, all three are great movies to own in your dvd collection and also it has Kevin Costner who is one of my favorite male actors.

 Great actor. Good films. Great price.
How in the H*** can anyone buy when there is no discription of what they are buying?
